Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave his secretary Monet's heart \Nback to him out of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respond.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As they say, if you are kind to people,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,good things will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you like it?\NThis Missile Girl's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...flame of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need this weapon?\NEven though you're a weapon woman yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for picking it up, Buffalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my good luck charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An owner of this weapon is \Ndestined to become happy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if you buy this, \Nyou'd make me happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely sure that he fooled you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm an invincible Iron Pirate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't fight for the peace of the sea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Iron Pirate!\N--How persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapon-morphosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revolver Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just made me itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's pretty tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Buffalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good!\NIt's collapsing faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The passage is gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a tunnel through a mountain.\NIf it collapses, we'll be buried alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it in a relaxed matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The wreckage blocked our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the brakes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:18:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe it! He saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to be my enemy!\NAlthough he already is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too comfortable yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadly gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that thing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it flowing in through \Ncracks of walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be more than \Njust being buried alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying such horrible things\Nin a cool manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is going to be \Ngas around the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anybody here generate wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so easy to find a person\Nwith such a special skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How easy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Young Master is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be in the room \Non the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh! He wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The window was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went out by himself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Tell me what's \Ngoing on over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-We've actually been blocked by\Nsome kind of iron guard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still safe there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, it is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:23:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the island and those squirts\Nhaven't been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,0:23:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of that guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
